snippet.title: Bionicle 2 : City of Legends | Unreleased Xbox Game
snippet.description:
A tech demo showing off the movement system of the unreleased sequel to the LEGO BIonicle game. Note : Do not adjust your speakers, there is no sound. Also note the Playstation 2 buttons, showing that it would continue on its multi-platform tradition.
